node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Tupac Shakur on September 03, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'THE TUPAC AMARU SHAKUR FOUNDATION, INC. Whats In Your Hand Black Man... Our hearts are with all those affected by Hurricane Ida. We understand how these disasters impact us physically, emotionally and mentally. Stay safe and please help someone in need. 4tasf'.

node.text:
“Our hearts are with all those affected by #HurricaneIda. Stay safe and please help someone in need. Donate to @covenanthousenola and any other organizations on the ground helping women, children and families during this difficult time. Thank You!”
- @4tasf
